Hello, welcome to Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. My name is Jerry Clark. How can I assist you today?

Hi Jerry, I was hoping to get some information about my billing. My name is Rose Williams.

Nice to meet you, Rose. Could you please provide me with your account number?

Sure, it's A B twelve three four.

Thank you, Rose. Just to verify, could you also tell me the last invoice amount you received?

I believe it was three five zero zero dollars.

Great, I've got your information here. Are there any specific billing questions you have?

Yes, I'm curious about the due dates and if there are any late fees.

Typically, invoices are due thirty days after issuance, and there is a small late fee of two percent.

Thanks, that's helpful to know.

You're welcome, Rose. If you have any more questions, feel free to reach out. Thank you for your time and have a great day!
